title: QuickPwn21-1.zip
description:
QuickPwn is a tool for quickly "pwning" an Apple iPhone or iPod Touch device.

QuickPwn differs from PwnageTool (PwnageTool is designed to custom build and tailor the ipsw production process).

QuickPwn 21-1 Supports 2.1 firmware with the unlocking and jailbreaking of iPhone 1st generation (2G) device. 

Supports the jailbreaking of iPod Touch 1st generation device and iPhone 3G. 


   * It does NOT support the unlocking of iPhone 3G 
   * It does NOT support the jailbreaking of second (newer) generation iPod Touch that is based around the n72ap.

Your device will need to be upgraded to 2.1 (using iTunes 8) before running this application.

The SHA1 sum for QuickPwn21-1.zip is f8124d0e8f31f64ef3272de8fbc679e1dd1f93a7
